{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":4000,"text":"Chris Anderson: William, hi. Good to see you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":6000,"text":"William Kamkwamba: Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":7000,"text":"CA: So, we've got a picture, I think? Where is this?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":12000,"text":"WK: This is my home. This is where I live."}]},{"cues":[{"time":16000,"text":"CA: Where? What country?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":18000,"text":"WK: In Malawi, Kasungu. In Kasungu. Yeah, Mala."}]},{"cues":[{"time":21000,"text":"CA: OK. Now, you're 19 now?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":24000,"text":"WK: Yeah. I'm 19 years now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":26000,"text":"CA: Five years ago you had an idea. What was that?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":29000,"text":"WK: I wanted to make a windmill."}]},{"cues":[{"time":31000,"text":"CA: A windmill?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":32000,"text":"WK: Yeah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":33000,"text":"CA: What, to power -- for lighting and stuff?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":37000,"text":"WK: Yeah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":39000,"text":"CA: So what did you do? How did you realize that?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":42000,"text":"WK: After I dropped out of school, I went to library,"},{"time":46000,"text":"and I read a book that would -- \"Using Energy,\""},{"time":50000,"text":"and I get information about doing the mill."},{"time":53000,"text":"And I tried, and I made it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":55000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":65000,"text":"CA: So you copied -- you exactly copied the design in the book."}]},{"cues":[{"time":69000,"text":"WK: Ah, no. I just --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":71000,"text":"CA: What happened?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":73000,"text":"WK: In fact, a design of the windmill that was in the book,"},{"time":77000,"text":"it has got four -- ah -- three blades,"},{"time":81000,"text":"and mine has got four blades."}]},{"cues":[{"time":84000,"text":"CA: The book had three, yours had four."}]},{"cues":[{"time":86000,"text":"WK: Yeah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":87000,"text":"CA: And you made it out of what?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":89000,"text":"WK: I made four blades, just because I want to increase power."}]},{"cues":[{"time":94000,"text":"CA: OK."}]},{"cues":[{"time":95000,"text":"WK: Yeah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":96000,"text":"CA: You tested three, and found that four worked better?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":98000,"text":"WK: Yeah. I test."}]},{"cues":[{"time":100000,"text":"CA: And what did you make the windmill out of?"},{"time":103000,"text":"What materials did you use?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":105000,"text":"WK: I use a bicycle frame, and a pulley, and plastic pipe, what then pulls --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":111000,"text":"CA: Do we have a picture of that? Can we have the next slide?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":114000,"text":"WK: Yeah. The windmill."}]},{"cues":[{"time":116000,"text":"CA: And so, and that windmill, what -- it worked?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":120000,"text":"WK: When the wind blows, it rotates and generates."}]},{"cues":[{"time":125000,"text":"CA: How much electricity?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":126000,"text":"WK: 12 watts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":128000,"text":"CA: And so, that lit a light for the house? How many lights?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":133000,"text":"WK: Four bulbs and two radios."}]},{"cues":[{"time":135000,"text":"CA: Wow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":136000,"text":"WK: Yeah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":137000,"text":"(Applause) CA: Next slide --"},{"time":147000,"text":"so who's that?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":149000,"text":"WK: This is my parents, holding the radio."}]},{"cues":[{"time":152000,"text":"CA: So what did they make of -- that you were 14, 15 at the time --"},{"time":156000,"text":"what did they make of this? They were impressed?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":159000,"text":"WK: Yeah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":160000,"text":"CA: And so what's your -- what are you going to do with this?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":162000,"text":"WK: Um --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":164000,"text":"CA: What do you -- I mean -- do you want to build another one?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":168000,"text":"WK: Yeah, I want to build another one --"},{"time":171000,"text":"to pump water and irrigation for crops."}]},{"cues":[{"time":176000,"text":"CA: So this one would have to be bigger?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":178000,"text":"WK: Yeah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":179000,"text":"CA: How big?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":180000,"text":"WK: I think it will produce more than 20 the watts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186000,"text":"CA: So that would produce irrigation for the entire village?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":190000,"text":"WK: Yeah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":192000,"text":"CA: Wow. And so you're talking to people here at TED"},{"time":195000,"text":"to get people who might be able to help in some way"},{"time":199000,"text":"to realize this dream?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":201000,"text":"WK: Yeah, if they can help me with materials, yeah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":205000,"text":"CA: And as you think of your life going forward,"},{"time":208000,"text":"you're 19 now,"},{"time":211000,"text":"do you picture continuing with this dream of working in energy?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":215000,"text":"WK: Yeah. I'm still thinking to work on energy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":220000,"text":"CA: Wow. William, it's a real honor to have you at the TED conference."},{"time":224000,"text":"Thank you so much for coming."}]},{"cues":[{"time":226000,"text":"WK: Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":228000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}